    "title": "Fishing, environment, and the erosion of a population portfolio",
    "authors": "Stier, A. C.; Olaf shelton, A.; Samhouri, J. F.; Feist, B. E.; Levin, P. S.",
    "year": 2020,
    "journal": "Ecosphere",
