    "title": "Defining ecosystem thresholds for human activities and environmental pressures in the California Current",
    "authors": "Samhouri, J. F.; Andrews, K. S.; Fay, G.; Harvey, C. J.; Hazen, E. L.; Hennessey, S. M.; Holsman, K.; Hunsicker, M. E.; Large, S. I.; Marshall, K. N.; Stier, A. C.; Tam, J. C.; Zador, S. G.",
    "year": 2017,
    "journal": "Ecosphere",
